Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.95,0:00:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Then may I have your name and number?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.16,0:00:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro Moritaka—
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.62,0:00:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're a pair?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.63,0:00:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and Takagi Akito.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.34,0:00:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have time tomorrow?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.05,0:00:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in middle school?
