Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.39,0:02:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.52,0:02:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you in advance.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.57,0:02:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an appointment tomorrow at 3 o'clock\Nwith Mr. Hattori who edits for Shounen Jack.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.91,0:02:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow? That's crazy.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.70,0:02:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess that's a publisher for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.04,0:02:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you want to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.37,0:02:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we'll be fine if we meet an hour early—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.50,0:02:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How about 1 o'clock, North Yakusa station?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.17,0:02:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Give or take—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.05,0:02:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.59,0:02:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go over the manuscript again.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.35,0:02:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let me check the dialogue again too.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.93,0:02:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Moritaka?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.23,0:02:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't come home yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.23,0:02:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He locked himself in his\Nroom as soon as he got home.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.65,0:02:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure hope he hasn't been \Npushing himself too much.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.07,0:02:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.37,0:03:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a mangaka must be awesome!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.46,0:03:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing your own drawings all lined up.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.46,0:03:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still just a gambler.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.80,0:03:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Gambler?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.88,0:03:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mangakas are the ones who can \Nmake a living off of only writing manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.76,0:03:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You either have to hit the jackpot right away
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.26,0:03:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,or write several fairly successful manga series.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of the folks are all just gambling.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.31,0:03:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The drawings are good but \NI don't know about my story.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.48,0:03:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The story's good but I'm not sure about my drawings.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.32,0:03:45.37,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Our—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.87,0:03:48.20,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,first manga—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.12,0:03:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're early!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.37,0:03:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you? Why're you—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.71,0:04:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, despite being sleep deprived, I woke up early.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.55,0:04:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.51,0:04:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't lay there doing nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.39,0:04:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother said to ask for next week's Jack.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.52,0:04:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way they'd give it to us.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.48,0:04:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother's at a good university, isn't he?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.95,0:04:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but he kind of gave up since he's not at his first choice school.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.03,0:04:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he just parties and does other extracurricular stuff,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.95,0:04:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,making the most of college life, I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.16,0:04:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Not much of a future.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.71,0:04:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why you wanted to be a mangaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.13,0:04:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I guess 'cause of my \Nparents, I didn't want a desk job.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.88,0:04:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad used to be a banker.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.76,0:04:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's late today too?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.81,0:04:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And brother?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.27,0:04:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be late because of prep school.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.44,0:04:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You had better study hard so \Nyou don't lose to your brother.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.90,0:05:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.73,0:05:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how did this semester's exams go?
