Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.36,0:05:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom taught at a high school, \Nso she made us study every day.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Great job, Akito!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.20,0:05:15.25,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm sure your father would be proud too.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.41,0:05:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like something got lost in the process of studying.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.67,0:05:19.79,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Do this well on the next ones, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's only in hindsight.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.71,0:05:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But then—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.88,0:05:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! How is that any different from \Nbeing fired for your boss's mistakes?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.26,0:05:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What else could I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.68,0:05:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What else—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.02,0:05:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what about us?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.27,0:05:38.31,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,What will become of us?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.89,0:05:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I didn't really understand what was going on at the time.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.19,0:05:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.07,0:05:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.45,0:05:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the groceries, Dad?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.70,0:05:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother asked me to.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.45,0:05:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna come with you next time!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure you can, next time.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.75,0:05:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a promise!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then in fifth grade—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.84,0:06:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Avenge—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.75,0:06:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:06.55,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur1.337\fnHelvetica Neue\c&H2F281D&\fs53.481\b1\pos(238.667,225.291)\frz17\fax0.3}Science
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You must—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.72,0:06:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,avenge your father, Acchan!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.51,0:06:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she mean by "avenge?"
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.28,0:06:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she want me to become the manger of some bank?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.27,0:06:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that why she made me study?
