Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.69,0:06:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Acchan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.82,0:06:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.49,0:06:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not your tool!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.78,0:06:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll decide my future myself!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.83,0:06:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,After that she became a better parent. She \Nnever says anything about my choices now.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.17,0:06:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. That was a pretty depressing story.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.93,0:06:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she knows about us becoming mangakas?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.47,0:06:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she knows, and she's okay with it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.10,0:06:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, just glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.48,0:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're smart, but I thought you just \Nrandomly decided to be a mangaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.57,0:07:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's kind of true.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.53,0:07:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we should probably get going now.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.16,0:07:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
