Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.75,0:07:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we're bringing in a \Nmanuscript while we're still in middle school.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.88,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\b1\blur1.003\fs37.437\fnHelvetica Neue\1c&HF9FFFf&\4c&HF9FFFF&\frz0\frx35\fax-0.32\move(399.333,-6.017,399.333,126.35,21,1814)}Yueisha
