Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.30,0:07:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone can bring a manuscript in.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.17,0:07:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What matters is how much they like it.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.76,0:07:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.19,0:07:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And what might be the purpose of your visit today?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.15,0:07:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Um— We wanted to submit a manuscript—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.36,0:07:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then please register at \Nthe reception desk over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.91,0:07:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Th—Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.83,0:07:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. How may I help you today?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.29,0:08:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here to submit a manuscript—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.33,0:08:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have an appointment?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.71,0:08:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Y—Yes, at 3 o'clock with \NMr. Hattori from Shounen Jack.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.09,0:08:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then could you please fill out this form for me?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.01,0:08:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Th—There are two of us, \Nso do we each fill one out?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.14,0:08:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, one form is enough for both of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.06,0:08:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,U—Um, I'm still a student \Nso for 'Company Name'—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.52,0:08:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, just write the name of your school.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.03,0:08:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry— I made a mistake.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.45,0:08:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just fill out a new form.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I—I'm done.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.32,0:08:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.24,0:08:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait just a second, please.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.00,0:08:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! However long it—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She said it'd be 'just a second'.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.29,0:08:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the reception desk.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Takagi and Mr. Mashiro are here to see you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.30,0:08:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.59,0:08:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your patience!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.63,0:08:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind waiting in the third \Ncubicle, Mr. Hattori will be with you shortly.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.55,0:08:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
