Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.81,0:18:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's work hard, here at Jack.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.65,0:18:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything comes up, just send \Nme an email at that address.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.50,0:18:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have much time, but I'll get \Nback to you as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.32,0:18:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be so thrilled \Nabout an email address.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.04,0:18:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd give out my cell phone \Nnumber when I find a golden egg.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.37,0:18:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are still just copper.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.42,0:18:36.47,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Not only did he give us his opinion, \Nhe's joking around with us too.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.47,0:18:38.26,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can trust him.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.26,0:18:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna submit this for our monthly \Nprize if that's alright with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.55,0:18:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.85,0:18:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,By monthly prize, you mean the prize that's \Nawarded each month to a chosen submission?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.81,0:18:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this going to win?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.52,0:18:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.23,0:18:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But people have different tastes,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.74,0:19:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,so maybe some will still consider this as a finalist.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.20,0:19:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, we don't always \Nknow what will or won't be a hit.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.08,0:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If we did, there wouldn't be so \Nmany new series that end quickly.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.13,0:19:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Predicting what'll be a hit is pretty much a gamble.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.97,0:19:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of the folks are all just gambling.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.85,0:19:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give me a call when \Nyour next manuscript's ready.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.68,0:19:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then—
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.77,0:19:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.23,0:19:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.11,0:19:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a success, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.37,0:19:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it was our first \Nmanuscript, we got an email address—
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.74,0:19:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you think, Shuujin?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.62,0:19:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.42,0:19:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Mr. Hattori's a good editor.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.67,0:20:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think so too.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.26,0:20:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how'd it go?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.39,0:20:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,With that middle school pair—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.51,0:20:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good enough. At least right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.43,0:20:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone can't be a Niizuma Eiji, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.40,0:20:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's only been using a pen for two months.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.74,0:20:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The script's still not quite palatable, \Nbut the idea itself is original—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.28,0:20:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So they sparked your interest?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.78,0:20:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Especially because they're still just 14.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.04,0:20:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.46,0:20:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Working as a pair isn't easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.42,0:20:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still kids so they could \Nget in a fight and break up.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.25,0:20:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But since you like them, \Nmake sure to raise them well.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.05,0:20:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they'll have surpassed \NNiizuma Eiji in three years.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.39,0:20:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You better pray you have a hit \Nin three years or you'll be fired.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.93,0:20:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.11,0:21:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Any noise annoys an oyster but a \Nnoisy noise annoys an oyster most.
