Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.86,0:21:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Unique New York. You know \Nyou need unique New York.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.58,0:21:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sally sells sea shells by the sea shore.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, summer break ends today.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.76,0:21:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And Saiko didn't hang out with us once!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.22,0:21:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I really wanted to see that x-rated one.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.68,0:21:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He was hanging out with Takagi the entire break.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.10,0:21:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they were going to prep school together.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.77,0:21:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe—
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.86,0:21:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna finish another story \Nbefore the end of the year.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.69,0:21:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And this time he won't say \Nit should be a light novel.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.40,0:21:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm gonna work on the things he \Nmentioned and make some amazing illustrations.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.37,0:21:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, the theme \Nof "The Two Earths" was too deep.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.91,0:21:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A question like 'What is truth?' \Nreally suits a novel better.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.08,0:22:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should've kept it \Nsomething more straightforward.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.05,0:22:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}do{\i0} get it.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.55,0:22:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so too.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.88,0:22:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You did? Then you should've told me sooner!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.13,0:22:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We agreed I wouldn't say \Na word about the names.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.93,0:22:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then next time, say whatever you're thinking.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.47,0:22:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's put in a lot of time on it and \Nproduce something we can both be proud of.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.06,0:22:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're okay with it, then I am.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.48,0:22:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:28.11,0:22:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:29.91,0:22:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how it was when I was in middle school.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.08,0:22:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,These are your seats for this trimester.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.13,0:22:44.09,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,What happens if my stomach \Ngrowls in the middle of class?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:49.34,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,The boring everyday gets to me sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:49.34,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,BETAAna genjitsu ni tsubusaretemo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:55.52,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I always get back on my feet, standing strong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:55.52,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,uchinomesareta jibun hiroiatsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.52,0:23:00.27,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times the end approaches me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.52,0:23:00.27,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,nando owari ga otazuneretemo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.27,0:23:06.61,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll push my own back forward, keeping me on my feet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.27,0:23:06.61,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,sono tabi ni jibun de jibun no senaka otoshita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:11.53,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I get lost in the meaning of continuing what I do,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:11.53,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,tsudzuiteku imi ni nayami
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:16.41,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll rid myself of those worries and keep myself going forward
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:16.41,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,sono mayoi sae tachikitte yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:17.58,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Always
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:17.58,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,itsumo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:22.71,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,The straight edge that draws the outline of my future
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:22.71,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,mirai no rinkakusen egaku massuguna jougi wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:28.38,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,is made of all the courage I've mustered up until today
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:28.38,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,ikutsumo no kinou no yuuki de dekiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:33.47,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll climb over the tall wall that I never thought I'd face,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:33.47,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,omoiegaita no to chigau takaikabe koe
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:39.52,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,and continue my journey, going past the vanishing point
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:39.52,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,shoushitsuten no mukou e susunde
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.77,0:23:45.69,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,This winding road seems to never end,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.77,0:23:45.69,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,harukanaru winding road
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.69,0:23:51.70,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it is the road I personally chose
